{"id": "Online advertentiemarkt blijft groeien__a2-late-chunking__0002", "text": "![Online advertising market keeps growing](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/media/tech_538_tcm16-66350.jpg)", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "Online advertentiemarkt blijft groeien__a2-late-chunking__0002", "source_slug": "Online advertentiemarkt blijft groeien", "source_title": "Online advertising market keeps growing", "source_url": null, "source_date": null, "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": null, "topic": null, "language_original": null, "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "gpt-5", "translated_with": null, "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 2, "n_chunks_total": 17, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-05-06", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 2}}
{"id": "Online advertentiemarkt blijft groeien__a2-late-chunking__0003", "text": "Economic conditions for the TMT sector have worsened. Growth of the Dutch economy is slowing and the economic indicators have turned less positive. The TMT sector is also affected by this, but it is still performing relatively well. You can read more about this in the state of TMT.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "Online advertentiemarkt blijft groeien__a2-late-chunking__0003", "source_slug": "Online advertentiemarkt blijft groeien", "source_title": "Online advertising market keeps growing", "source_url": null, "source_date": null, "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": null, "topic": null, "language_original": null, "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "gpt-5", "translated_with": null, "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 3, "n_chunks_total": 17, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-05-06", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 3}}
{"id": "Online advertentiemarkt blijft groeien__a2-late-chunking__0004", "text": "(Can’t see a download or unable to download the report? Then upgrade your browser to the most recent version.)", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "Online advertentiemarkt blijft groeien__a2-late-chunking__0004", "source_slug": "Online advertentiemarkt blijft groeien", "source_title": "Online advertising market keeps growing", "source_url": null, "source_date": null, "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": null, "topic": null, "language_original": null, "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "gpt-5", "translated_with": null, "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 4, "n_chunks_total": 17, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-05-06", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 4}}
{"id": "Online advertentiemarkt blijft groeien__a2-late-chunking__0005", "text": "1 MB](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/media/Stand-van-TMT-juli-2019-1_tcm16-66349.pdf)", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "Online advertentiemarkt blijft groeien__a2-late-chunking__0005", "source_slug": "Online advertentiemarkt blijft groeien", "source_title": "Online advertising market keeps growing", "source_url": null, "source_date": null, "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": null, "topic": null, "language_original": null, "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "gpt-5", "translated_with": null, "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 5, "n_chunks_total": 17, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-05-06", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 5}}
{"id": "Online advertentiemarkt blijft groeien__a2-late-chunking__0006", "text": "The economic climate has become less favourable for the TMT sector. Exports are falling sharply and this in particular is causing a growth slowdown for the Dutch economy as a whole. Producer confidence is lower than before, but has stabilised at a still-high level. Other indicators such as consumer confidence and the purchasing managers’ index have clearly deteriorated.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "Online advertentiemarkt blijft groeien__a2-late-chunking__0006", "source_slug": "Online advertentiemarkt blijft groeien", "source_title": "Online advertising market keeps growing", "source_url": null, "source_date": null, "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": null, "topic": null, "language_original": null, "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "gpt-5", "translated_with": null, "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 6, "n_chunks_total": 17, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-05-06", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 6}}
{"id": "Online advertentiemarkt blijft groeien__a2-late-chunking__0007", "text": "## Staff shortage remains the biggest obstacle for the TMT sector", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "Online advertentiemarkt blijft groeien__a2-late-chunking__0007", "source_slug": "Online advertentiemarkt blijft groeien", "source_title": "Online advertising market keeps growing", "source_url": null, "source_date": null, "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": null, "topic": null, "language_original": null, "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "gpt-5", "translated_with": null, "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 7, "n_chunks_total": 17, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-05-06", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 7}}
{"id": "Online advertentiemarkt blijft groeien__a2-late-chunking__0008", "text": "Business confidence in the TMT sector has fallen in recent quarters, but at 13.7 it is still high. No fewer than 52% of entrepreneurs say they experience no significant obstacles. The main obstacle remains the shortage of workers, which 31% are affected by.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "Online advertentiemarkt blijft groeien__a2-late-chunking__0008", "source_slug": "Online advertentiemarkt blijft groeien", "source_title": "Online advertising market keeps growing", "source_url": null, "source_date": null, "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": null, "topic": null, "language_original": null, "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "gpt-5", "translated_with": null, "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 8, "n_chunks_total": 17, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-05-06", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 8}}
{"id": "Online advertentiemarkt blijft groeien__a2-late-chunking__0009", "text": "The online advertising market grew further last year and is taking an ever larger share of total net media spending. This is at the expense of print media, which are seeing their share of media spending shrink.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "Online advertentiemarkt blijft groeien__a2-late-chunking__0009", "source_slug": "Online advertentiemarkt blijft groeien", "source_title": "Online advertising market keeps growing", "source_url": null, "source_date": null, "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": null, "topic": null, "language_original": null, "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "gpt-5", "translated_with": null, "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 9, "n_chunks_total": 17, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-05-06", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 9}}
{"id": "Online advertentiemarkt blijft groeien__a2-late-chunking__0010", "text": "Read our forecasts in the full report ‘State of TMT’.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "Online advertentiemarkt blijft groeien__a2-late-chunking__0010", "source_slug": "Online advertentiemarkt blijft groeien", "source_title": "Online advertising market keeps growing", "source_url": null, "source_date": null, "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": null, "topic": null, "language_original": null, "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "gpt-5", "translated_with": null, "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 10, "n_chunks_total": 17, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-05-06", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 10}}
